## Level 1: System Context

The System Context diagram shows the big picture of the system landscape.

```mermaid
C4Context
    title System Context Diagram - {{ project_name | default("System") }}
    
    {% for actor in actors | default([]) %}
    Person({{ actor.id }}, "{{ actor.name }}", "{{ actor.description }}")
    {% endfor %}
    
    System(mainSystem, "{{ project_name | default('System') }}", "{{ system_description | default('Main system under development') }}")
    
    {% for external in external_systems | default([]) %}
    System_Ext({{ external.id }}, "{{ external.name }}", "{{ external.description }}")
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% for db in external_databases | default([]) %}
    SystemDb_Ext({{ db.id }}, "{{ db.name }}", "{{ db.description }}")
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% for rel in context_relationships | default([]) %}
    Rel({{ rel.from }}, {{ rel.to }}, "{{ rel.description }}"{{ ', "' + rel.technology + '"' if rel.technology else '' }})
    {% endfor %}
```

